---
title: Salt & Pepper Pork with Honey-Soy Veggies, Garlic Rice & Japanese Mayo
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our pork version is going to steal even your biggest fans! With all the umami, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-salt-pepper-pork-5c532145.jpg
